original: Lindberg, Marta Alexandra (Sandra), läroverksadjunkt, Karlshamn, f. 17/2/93 i Ahus, Krist. 1., av stat:förest. P. L. o. Marta Flygare. — Stud:ex. i Lund 10, fil. mag. 16, provår 19-20. Vik. folksk :lär. i Olseröd 11, e. o. folksk :lär. i Anderslöv 16-19, lär. i Djursholm 20-21, ord. ämneslär. v. Ystads h. folksk. 21, adj. i matem., fysik o. kemi v. Karlshamns samrealsL sed. 31, tillsyn :lär. sed. 31.
translated: Lindberg, Marta Alexandra (Sandra), high school teacher, Karlshamn, b. 17/2/93 in Ahus, Kristianstad County, daughter of government official P. L. and Marta Flygare. — Completed high school in Lund in 1910, earned a Bachelor of Arts in 1916, probationary year in 1919-1920. Temporary elementary school teacher in Olseröd from 1911, temporary elementary school teacher in Anderslöv from 1916-1919, teacher in Djursholm from 1920-1921, regular subject teacher at Ystad's secondary elementary school in 1921, math, physics, and chemistry teacher at Karlshamn's secondary school since 1931, supervisor teacher since 1931.
